Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.60,0:01:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再被杀死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.40,0:01:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.00,0:02:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 不能凭感情杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.80,0:02:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐会被送下地狱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.10,0:02:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那样也无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.80,0:02:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 内心被憎恨支配了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.10,0:02:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.10,0:02:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.30,0:02:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.60,0:02:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨 流向地狱就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.70,0:03:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.60,0:03:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.70,0:03:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一 我好难受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.90,0:03:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了啊 仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭团已经做好了 吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.80,0:04:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又帮别人做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事爸爸你根本不用做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.80,0:04:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.10,0:04:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你至少收点钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身体不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.00,0:04:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干农活又总是给村里添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也就当作是谢谢大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.70,0:04:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.60,0:05:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完了我来帮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.10,0:05:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 你去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才小爱来过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你在睡觉就说等会儿再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就算了 帮您做草鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.70,0:05:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去陪她玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.70,0:05:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能陪小爱玩的除了你这表兄就没有别人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.90,0:05:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.40,0:05:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 又被人欺负了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.30,0:05:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁 是耕吉吗 那个混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来 仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.90,0:05:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耕吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.10,0:05:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么 仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴 是他把小爱弄哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 那个家伙可是妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.40,0:05:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么护着她是想干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.40,0:05:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.40,0:06:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有她在就会有可怕的事情发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.30,0:06:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天她把死去的蝴蝶放在手上它就活过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是妖怪的力量 不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.90,0:06:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.80,0:06:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里的人们也觉得害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.50,0:06:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要爱在村里一定会倒大霉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让她消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了村子消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.00,0:06:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护着爱的家伙不是村里的伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.90,0:06:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那蝴蝶还没死 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意那些家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.50,0:07:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.90,0:07:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不觉得你是妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱就是小爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.10,0:07:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚你们的女儿将为了今后七年的五谷丰登
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献给山神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是非常光荣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.80,0:08:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在神社等着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.20,0:08:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了就过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.60,0:08:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是小爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小爱是妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们这么想 对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.40,0:08:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.60,0:08:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为感到害怕 希望她消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把小爱选作送七的巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.90,0:08:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家只是希望把小爱赶出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.90,0:08:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你把能代替她的人带来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.90,0:08:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在外面等 快点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.00,0:08:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事情拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.00,0:09:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 带着净化的身心去山神那儿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.70,0:09:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么做给村里的人知道的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.30,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到山神的愤怒 我也知道那事是不能做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.50,0:10:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.90,0:10:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去小爱就太可怜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 保护爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.30,0:10:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.80,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.00,0:10:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点 冷死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护小爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.60,0:11:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴天太少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.70,0:11:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.00,0:11:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有好好向山神祈祷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 今晚也拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.40,0:11:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.40,0:12:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把换洗的衣服和吃的带来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.00,0:12:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.00,0:12:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑在一起也不够交年贡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.60,0:12:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.10,0:12:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有用仓库的干粟米凑数了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.20,0:12:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么做的话我们吃什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.30,0:13:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一直都是这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.80,0:13:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是饿坏了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.00,0:13:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她妈没奶水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.30,0:13:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.90,0:13:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样可能撑不过这个冬天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.00,0:13:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱树之花 何时绽放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.50,0:13:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山麓庄中 何时绽放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.10,0:13:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱树之花 何时芬芳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.50,0:13:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七子颜笑 玩耍时常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.10,0:13:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱树之花 何时飘荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.60,0:13:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七子咏歌 沉入梦乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.20,0:13:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱树之花 何时凋亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.90,0:14:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七子逝去 魂升天上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.50,0:14:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.60,0:14:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.80,0:14:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的月夜溜出祠堂不要紧吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.30,0:14:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.40,0:14:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里人脑子里全是收成的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.60,0:14:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.60,0:14:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.60,0:14:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.60,0:14:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.20,0:14:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一直这样就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.00,0:15:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.00,0:15:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起离开村子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.70,0:15:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.80,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.10,0:15:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎 你干了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.40,0:15:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.90,0:15:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流言都传开了 说你每天晚上进山里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.70,0:15:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样什么都清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.30,0:15:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄稼没有收成就是因为她违反了规矩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.60,0:15:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招来了山神的愤怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.00,0:15:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里的人现在都饿成什么样子了 你有没有想过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.40,0:15:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 你这样的女孩不能原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.40,0:16:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 爱 逃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.40,0:16:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.70,0:16:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.70,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.30,0:16:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 爸爸 放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.50,0:16:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让她跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.80,0:16:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.10,0:16:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命 仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.90,0:16:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.90,0:16:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.90,0:16:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.60,0:16:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真恨自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明想救小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.40,0:16:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的发生了事情却什么都做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.50,0:16:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有被小姐收容 我们差点就烂在地狱里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们欠小姐个大人情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪儿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.80,0:17:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道真的下地狱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.40,0:17:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 冷静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.90,0:17:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慌张也是没有办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.80,0:17:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说世事只有顺其自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.60,0:17:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.40,0:17:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.50,0:17:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动 待着听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.00,0:17:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么下去 爱她 爱她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.20,0:17:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也帮他们违反了村里的规矩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.80,0:17:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想死吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再随便胡来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不是你一个人能承担的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.00,0:17:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.40,0:17:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱她自己之前不是已经答应过了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.80,0:17:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.40,0:17:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈求山神的原谅 只能这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.10,0:17:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忍忍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.10,0:17:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.20,0:17:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.90,0:18:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.80,0:18:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.30,0:18:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快填土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.00,0:18:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎 开动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.00,0:18:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎 赎去这六年你欺瞒山神的罪孽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.70,0:18:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须赎罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.50,0:18:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.90,0:18:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了村子 这样下去大家都会饿死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.60,0:18:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.80,0:19:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.20,0:19:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子变成这样都是你和爱的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点谢罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.00,0:19:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再没有奶水的话 也活不下去几天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.70,0:19:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.70,0:19:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了村子快动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.40,0:19:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你会保护我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那么相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.30,0:19:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.90,0:19:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来填土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.10,0:19:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.60,0:20:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山神 违反了规矩的女孩已经这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.60,0:20:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请救救村子 救救村子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.90,0:20:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨你们 所有的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了也不放过你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.40,0:21:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.90,0:21:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱树之花 何时绽放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.70,0:21:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山麓庄中 何时绽放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.90,0:21:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.30,0:21:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱树之花 何时芬芳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.00,0:21:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七子颜笑 玩耍时常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.00,0:22:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.30,0:22:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.50,0:22:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.30,0:22:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.30,0:22:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
