Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.70,0:24:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.00,0:24:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.40,0:24:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.80,0:24:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.80,0:24:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身也要付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.20,0:24:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
